And then, when using `DjangoObjectType` (if we want to customize without touching the settings file)

```python
class MyType(DjangoObjectType):
    class Meta:
        db_using = "secondary-other" # Will be settings.GRAPHENE['DEFAULT_QUERY_DATABASE'] otherwise by default

class MyMutation(DjangoModelFormMutation):
    class Meta:
        db_using = "primary-other" # Will be settings.GRAPHENE['DEFAULT_MUTATION_DATABASE'] otherwise by default
```

